OL,3,CBristol's biggest homeless shelter
OL,4,Copens for Christmas period
OL,6,FITV News' Robert Murphy spoke to
OL,7,Fvolunteers and organisers from Caring
OL,8,Fin Bristol
OL,10,FA team of 400 volunteers is running
OL,11,Fthe West Country's biggest Christmas
OL,12,Fhomeless project which has once again
OL,13,Fopened its doors to those in need over
OL,14,Fthe festive period.
OL,16,FThe Trinity Centre has been taken over
OL,17,Fby Caring in Bristol to cater for 700
OL,18,Fhomeless men and women in the city
OL,19,Fover the next seven days.
