OL,6,FThe centre will feature a Christmas
OL,7,Flunch overseen by Michelin-starred
OL,8,Fchef Josh Eggleton, as well as a
OL,9,F'personal shopping experience' and a
OL,10,Fcinema.
OL,12,FCaring in Bristol's Alv Hirst, said:
OL,13,F"To experience homelessness is a real
OL,14,Fpersonal disaster. This time of year
OL,15,Fis cold.
