OL,3,CBristol's biggest homeless shelter
OL,4,Copens for Christmas period
OL,6,F"There are people shopping and doing
OL,7,Fall the things that we do at Christmas
OL,8,Fand people just feel that they don't
OL,9,Fbelong anymore. And we really want to
OL,10,Fcreate that situation where people can
OL,11,Ffeel that they belong."
OL,13,FCaring in Bristol says the cost of
OL,14,Fliving crisis, high interest rates and
OL,15,Fhigh property prices in Bristol have
OL,16,Fall fuelled a rise in homeless numbers
OL,17,Fin the city.
OL,19,F"It's a very, very difficult landscape
OL,20,Fout there," said Mijanou Blech, CEO of
OL,21,FCaring in Bristol.
