OL,3,CBristol's biggest homeless shelter
OL,4,Copens for Christmas period
OL,6,F"There are many, many people that are
OL,7,Ffinding themselves without a safe home
OL,8,Fat the moment. Anybody can experience
OL,9,Fhomelessness and we're here to kind of
OL,10,Fsupport anybody that does."
OL,12,FThe centre offers food and shelter
OL,13,Ffrom 10am-4pm, as well as a cinema and
OL,14,Fthe chance to speak with people.
OL,16,FThis year has also seen the addition
OL,17,Fof a 'personal shopping experience'
OL,18,Finnovation which allows people to get
OL,19,Fnew clothes.
