OL,4,Copens for Christmas period
OL,6,FAbby Carter, a volunteer at the
OL,7,Fservice, said: :They can get a new
OL,8,Fjacket, get some trousers, get a belt,
OL,9,Fthey might need a new rucksack,
OL,10,Fwhatever they're after, really, to
OL,11,Fkeep them clothed.
OL,13,F"It is going to get chilly as the
OL,14,FWinter goes on."
OL,16,FOther services available at the space
OL,17,Finclude massage, music entertainment,
OL,18,Fart and repairs.
